ort is key.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBut we also love pieces that are multi-functional. Cult’s \u003ca href=\"https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/directory/product/riviera-lounge\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eRiviera lounge\u003c/a\u003e is the perfect example, instead of expanding length ways like a traditional sun lounger, its expansion is in its width allowing it to serve as a chair and table, a sofa or a sun bed.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eKing Living’s \u003ca href=\"https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/directory/product/plateau-outdoor-sofa-sun-lounge\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003ePlateau outdoor sofa and sun lounge\u003c/a\u003e serves a similar function, with multi-directional seating and modular flexibility to accommodate entertaining and lounging alike. The Omni Positional Backrests in the middle of the sofa also allow for dual seating — perfect for parties.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFor those pieces that offer the ultimate comfort, check out ELLISON STUDIOS. \u003ca href=\"https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/directory/product/alva-outdoor-2-seat-sofa\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eAlva outdoor 2 seat sofa\u003c/a\u003e and Tait’s \u003ca href=\"https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/directory/product/trace-sofa\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eTrace sofa\u003c/a\u003e, both of which bring chic indoor style to the outdoors.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"NaN\" height=\"NaN\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"50vw\" srcset=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/BenSelke-tdf-homes6.jpg\u0026amp;w=384\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 384w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/BenSelke-tdf-homes6.jpg\u0026amp;w=768\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 768w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/BenSelke-tdf-homes6.jpg\u0026amp;w=1440\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 1440w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/BenSelke-tdf-homes6.jpg\u0026amp;w=1920\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 1920w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/BenSelke-tdf-homes6.jpg\u0026amp;w=2560\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 2560w\" src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/BenSelke-tdf-homes6.jpg\u0026amp;w=2560\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"NaN\" height=\"NaN\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"50vw\" srcset=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/outdoorfurniture-tdf-directory.jpg\u0026amp;w=384\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 384w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/outdoorfurniture-tdf-directory.jpg\u0026amp;w=768\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 768w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/outdoorfurniture-tdf-directory.jpg\u0026amp;w=1440\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 1440w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/outdoorfurniture-tdf-directory.jpg\u0026amp;w=1920\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 1920w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/outdoorfurniture-tdf-directory.jpg\u0026amp;w=2560\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 2560w\" src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/outdoorfurniture-tdf-directory.jpg\u0026amp;w=2560\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"NaN\" height=\"NaN\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"50vw\" srcset=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Koala-tdf-outdoor13.jpg\u0026amp;w=384\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 384w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Koala-tdf-outdoor13.jpg\u0026amp;w=768\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 768w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Koala-tdf-outdoor13.jpg\u0026amp;w=1440\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 1440w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Koala-tdf-outdoor13.jpg\u0026amp;w=1920\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 1920w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Koala-tdf-outdoor13.jpg\u0026amp;w=2560\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 2560w\" src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Koala-tdf-outdoor13.jpg\u0026amp;w=2560\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"NaN\" height=\"NaN\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"50vw\" srcset=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AllisonLewis-tdf-homes7.jpg\u0026amp;w=384\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 384w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AllisonLewis-tdf-homes7.jpg\u0026amp;w=768\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 768w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AllisonLewis-tdf-homes7.jpg\u0026amp;w=1440\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 1440w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AllisonLewis-tdf-homes7.jpg\u0026amp;w=1920\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 1920w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AllisonLewis-tdf-homes7.jpg\u0026amp;w=2560\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 2560w\" src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AllisonLewis-tdf-homes7.jpg\u0026amp;w=2560\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch3\u003eSmall Spaces\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEven small outdoor spaces can go big with outdoor entertaining, you just need the right pieces!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOutdoor chairs like Tait’s \u003ca href=\"https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/directory/product/swing-chair\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eSwing chair\u003c/a\u003e, Trit House’s \u003ca href=\"https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/directory/product/fermob-bistro-metal-chair\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eFermob Bistro metal chair\u003c/a\u003e, Thonet’s \u003ca href=\"https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/directory/product/tolix-patio-armchair\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eTolix patio armchair\u003c/a\u003e and Cult’s \u003ca href=\"https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/directory/product/palissade-lounge-chair-low\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003ePalissade lounge chair\u003c/a\u003e have a lightweight and streamlined design that allow the eye (and light) to move through, adding to the illusion of space.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBean bags are another great option for smaller spaces as they’re so versatile and can be moved around easily. We’re particularly drawn to \u003ca href=\"https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/directory/product/bean-bag\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eBasil Bangs’ bean bag\u003c/a\u003e with its L-shaped form for ultimate relaxation.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" loading=\"