0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 2560w\" src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/outdoorfurniture-tdf-directory4.jpg\u0026amp;w=2560\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch3\u003eAccessories\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNo space is complete without accessories — this goes for outdoor areas too.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFor evenings outdoors, create some soft ambient light with We Ponder’s \u003ca href=\"https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/directory/product/dawn-short-exterior\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eDawn short exterior sconces\u003c/a\u003e, which cast a gentle light against the walls of your home from its eye-catching ceramic silhouette. Cult’s \u003ca href=\"https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/directory/product/obello-portable-table-lamp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eObello portable table lamp\u003c/a\u003e is another great and more versatile option, with its iconic mushroom shape and rechargeable capabilities.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFinish off big and small spaces alike with side tables that not only look great, but also provide easy perches for beverages, books and sunscreen. For something more sculptural, look to Cult’s \u003ca href=\"https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/directory/product/bowler-side-table\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eBowler side table\u003c/a\u003e, and for a pop of colour, Fearon’s \u003ca href=\"https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/directory/product/chub-table\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eChub table\u003c/a\u003e is an instant winner.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb data-stringify-type=\"bold\"\u003e\u003ci data-stringify-type=\"italic\"\u003eWant to see more? Visit \u003c/i\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cb data-stringify-type=\"bold\"\u003e\u003ci data-stringify-type=\"italic\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/di